Package: earthquakes
Type: Package
Title: Visualize the NOAA significant earthquake date
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Damian Brunold
Maintainer: Damian Brunold <damian.brunold@bluewin.ch>
Description: Loads and cleans the NOAA significant earthquake data
    and provides ggplot and leaflet functions for visualizing the data
    using a timeline, optionally with labels, or using a leaflet map.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
